2054.subject: HPWE
2054.descrlong: Focuses on top-roped rock climbing and bouldering.  Covers equipment, techniques and training.  Includes knots, anchor systems, belaying, rappelling, and risk assessment.  Held outdoors and requires one weekend trip. Course fee required.
